{"tid":29630,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"真係我問題咩？","createTime":"2016-12-08T16:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T17:59:34.000Z","uid":59790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5974be73c3c2d76aa98031a32a10ddd176118467","tid":29630,"uid":59790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:27:50.000Z","msg":"小弟本身平時都冇乜野講同唔鍾意講電話，但你話想每晚都傾<br />\nok冇問題，咁我咪打囉<br />\n<br />\n每晚最小都傾成幾個字，傾到我冇曬話題有小小dead air先收線<br />\n咁都俾你話我唔想同陪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬呀，每日返工放工都已經由朝見到晚，有時仲要一晚講幾次電話<br />\n邊有咁多野講呀<br />\n<br />\n我已經好努力去開話題，你又話我無聊<br />\n係咪真係我問題呀？"},{"pid":"48a791f0306ec865d0797ea797c623a90d78aa9a","tid":29630,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:28:50.000Z","msg":"有女就"},{"pid":"d370cd646236b3d2706ac45a4438141c37af0e29","tid":29630,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟同事拍拖 你會後悔的"},{"pid":"d99f3c315da4eb1c85237876c2499b33d63f8450","tid":29630,"uid":59790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟同事拍拖 你會後悔的</blockquote><br />\n平時面對面嘅時候，我地又冇問題喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係一分開，佢就成日都黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c726bf0aa579256ed9d846ae97c7da3840f5229","tid":29630,"uid":16880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"係咪無安全感呀 驚一番到屋企你就搵第二條女"},{"pid":"869bf8a238748057f473d0f8af1506f839046c1b","tid":29630,"uid":59790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:53:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪無安全感呀 驚一番到屋企你就搵第二條女</blockquote><br />\n佢知我唔會，我覺得係佢慣左可以同啲朋友由朝傾到晚都唔停<br />\n<br />\n但又唔諗下我唔係佢班朋友，佢地個個都勁多野講<br />\n<br />\n我只係個內向毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925eec2b77920681ae5a7f21f91086efadfe7e68","tid":29630,"uid":58022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:00:59.000Z","msg":"樓主無問題呀<br />\n我係絲 我都唔太鐘意傾電話<br />\n個人喜好姐"},{"pid":"45f5fd4a50816dd633564077666a61b2b9d1075d","tid":29630,"uid":59790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主無問題呀<br />\n我係絲 我都唔太鐘意傾電話<br />\n個人喜好姐</blockquote><br />\n多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜佢唔係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉係咁聽悔氣說話，仲單剔埋添<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d86a4ab90ae6731f56e98a5519df178ddb1d9d9","tid":29630,"uid":37205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:16:04.000Z","msg":"same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nex好鐘意講電話，但我無嘢好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到成日deadair佢就話我係未好唔想陪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n面對面溝通完全無問題，係一傾電話就會嗌交，我到而家都好憎傾電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9afa6cd16c3f0c0f93b2a33b6b65e16c31269b4f","tid":29630,"uid":59790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nex好鐘意講電話，但我無嘢好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到成日deadair佢就話我係未好唔想陪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n面對面溝通完全無問題，係一傾電話就會嗌交，我到而家都好憎傾電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地永遠唔覺自己有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔憎傾電話呀，但有deadair嘅時候一係開新話題，一係收線唔好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d20d5bcc9aa188ab842f79115906225e7f6abd","tid":29630,"uid":59790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:28:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地永遠唔覺自己有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔憎傾電話呀，但有deadair嘅時候一係開新話題，一係收線唔好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係已經由朝見到晚喇大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8af8e80d34450dba71aaf8f37ad6c16582aef3","tid":29630,"uid":52419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:30:59.000Z","msg":"樓主冇問題<br />\n我電話長期靜音<br />\n聽電話完全靠緣份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46521571e1bda487f9dddc9a511ccde6f4d289e","tid":29630,"uid":59790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:37:27.000Z","msg":"有話題咪係咁講，冇咪大家聽下對方把聲講下早抖<br />\n<br />\n洗唔洗話唔再聽我電話呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89107da2ec6b39eb40ba36ffc38c33244a16a59d","tid":29630,"uid":59830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:59:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}